n the server file, including the import.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will create `/server.ts` to implement our full-stack server. It will handle the static assets, mount Vite\'s middleware, and expose server-side endpoints for our mock-proof interactive features:\n- AI-Generated Personalized Roadmap\n- AI profile grading (LinkedIn/CV) with structured scores and custom rewrites\n- Dynamic guestbook to read & persist mentorship testimonials\n- Dynamic booking system that validates and assigns confirmation codes.\n\nIt implements a defensive pattern: if `GEMINI_API_KEY` is not present, it logs a clean status and provides high-intelligence fallback simulations so that development and preview remain fully functional while warning about configuration."
