    modified_response: "I will now create `/src/components/RoadmapBuilder.tsx` to build the interactive Career Diagnostic quiz. It collects:\n- High school/College stages\n- Desired developmental roles (Front-End, Back-End, Mobile, Data, Game dev)\n- Challenges.\nIt presents a custom step selector, and upon clicking \"Generar Ruta de Aprendizaje\", calls our server\'s safe `/api/gemini/roadmap` route, retrieving a full career plan. This is styled as a detailed, step-by-step visual roadmap tree with Kuni\'s custom mentor advice, and a customizable \"Print / Save Plan\" utility."
