    modified_response: "I will now create the interactive `/src/components/BookingCalendar.tsx` scheduler component. It guides software candidates through booking a session with Kuni (S/ 30):\n- Step 1: Select their study/tech motive (Secondary, Uni cycle, Reconversion, etc.)\n- Step 2: Choose a mock date and timeslot\n- Step 3: Fill out details (e.g., email, Discord tag, questions)\n- Step 4: Submit to our `/api/bookings/create` endpoint. Upon confirmation, the backend assigns a confirmation code which is formatted on screen as a ticket."
